high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge to your left.
take the soapbar on the side.
Turn around left side of the sink.
Put the soapbar in the water and clean it.
Take the soap and turn the toilet on the left side.
Put it on the soapbar in the toilet place.
anns.task_desc: Take SoapBar and clean the Toilet side

high_descs: turn around go straight and turn left to reach the fridge.
pick up the soapbar from the clean item on the wooden rack
clean item on the wooden rack, turn around, go straight, and turn left to the sink.
Put the soapbar into the sink, clean it off, and pick it back up.
Turn and head towards the toilet near to the bathtub.
Place the soapbar into the clean item, the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Place the SoapBar into clean Toilet

high_descs: Turn left and go near to the fridge.
Take the soapbar from the fridge
Turn right then turn left to enter the sink.
Put the soapbar in the sink, pour the water and take it back.
Place the soapbar on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Take the SoapBar from the fridge and Place the SoapBar on top of the Toilet
